\c 14
\s Ubuqhawe bukaJonathani
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi \add ngolunye\add* usuku, uJonathani indodana kaSawuli wathi emfaneni othwala izikhali zakhe: Woza sichaphele ebuthweni lenqaba yamaFilisti elingaphetsheya ngale. Kodwa kamtshelanga uyise.
\v 2 USawuli wayehlala-ke ephethelweni leGibeya\x + Josh. 18.28.\x* ngaphansi kwesihlahla \w sepomegranati\w**\x + Hlu. 4.5. Hlu. 20.45,47.\x* esiseMigironi\x + Isa. 10.28.\x*; labantu ababelaye babengaphose babe ngamadoda angamakhulu ayisithupha\x + 13.15.\x*;
\v 3 loAhiya, indodana kaAhitubi, umfowabo kaIkabodi, indodana kaPhinehasi, indodana kaEli\x + 4.21.\x*, umpristi weN\nd kosi\nd* eShilo\x + Josh. 18.1.\x*, wayembethe \w i-efodi\w**. Kodwa abantu babengazi ukuthi uJonathani uhambile\x + 2.28.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Laphakathi kwemikhandlo, lapho uJonathani ayezama ukuchapha khona ukuya ebuthweni lenqaba yamaFilisti, kwakuledwala elicijileyo nganeno, ledwala elicijileyo ngaphetsheya; njalo ibizo lelinye laliyiBozezi, lebizo lelinye laliyiSene\x + 13.23.\x*.
\v 5 Elinye iliwa laligxile enyakatho maqondana leMikimashi\x + 2. 8.\x*, lelinye ngeningizimu maqondana leGeba\x + 13.16.\x*.
\v 6 UJonathani wasesithi emfaneni othwala izikhali zakhe: Woza sichaphele ebuthweni lenqaba \add e\add*lalaba abangasokanga\x + Hlu. 14.3.\x*; mhlawumbe iN\nd kosi\nd* izasisebenzela, ngoba kakulasenqabelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ukusindisa ngabanengi loba ngabalutshwana\x + Hlu. 7.4,7. 2 Lan. 14.11.\x*.
\v 7 Umthwali wezikhali zakhe wasesithi kuye: Yenza konke okusenhliziyweni yakho; phambuka, khangela ngilawe njengokwenhliziyo yakho.
\v 8 UJonathani wasesithi: Khangela, sizachaphela kulabobantu sizibonakalise kibo.
\v 9 Uba bekhuluma njalo kithi \add besithi\add*: Manini mpo, size sifike kini; sizakuma-ke endaweni yethu, singenyukeli kibo.
\v 10 Kodwa uba bekhuluma njalo kithi \add besithi\add*: Yenyukelani kithi; sizakwenyuka-ke, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ibanikele esandleni sethu\x + 13.12.\x*; lalokhu kuzakuba yisibonakaliso kithi\x + Gen. 24.14. Hlu. 7.11.\x*.
\v 11 Ngakho bobabili bazibonakalisa ebuthweni lenqaba yamaFilisti; amaFilisti asesithi: Khangelani, amaHebheru asephuma emilindini abecatshe kiyo\x + 13.6.\x*.
\v 12 Amadoda ebutho lenqaba asephendula oJonathani lomthwali wezikhali zakhe athi: Yenyukelani kithi, sizalitshengisa ulutho. UJonathani wasesithi kumthwali wezikhali zakhe: Yenyuka ungilandele, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* iwanikele esandleni sikaIsrayeli.
\v 13 UJonathani wasekhwela ngezandla zakhe langenyawo zakhe, lomthwali wezikhali zakhe emva kwakhe. Asesiwa phambi kukaJonathani, lomthwali wezikhali zakhe wawabulala emva kwakhe.
\v 14 Ukutshaya kokuqala atshaya ngakho uJonathani lomthwali wezikhali zakhe kwakungaba phose ngamadoda angamatshumi amabili, ensimini elingana lengxenye yendima yesipani.
\v 15 Kwasekusiba khona ukuthuthumela enkambeni, egangeni, laphakathi kwabantu bonke; ibutho lenqaba labachithi labo bathuthumela, lomhlaba wanyikinyeka, kwasekusiba yikuthuthumela okukhulu\x + 13.17.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Abalindi bakaSawuli eGibeya yakoBhenjamini\x + Josh. 18.28.\x* basebebona ukuthi, khangela, ixuku lancibilika\x + Josh. 2.9.\x* lihamba litshayel\add an\add*a phansi\x + 14.19,20. Isa. 16.8.\x*.
\v 17 USawuli wasesithi ebantwini ababelaye: Ake libale, libone ukuthi ngubani osuke kithi. Kwathi sebebalile, khangela, uJonathani lomthwali wezikhali zakhe babengekho.
\v 18 USawuli wasesithi kuAhiya: Letha lapha umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu. Ngoba umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu ngalolosuku wawukubantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 19 Kwasekusithi uSawuli esakhuluma lompristi, umsindo owawusenkambeni yamaFilisti waqhubeka wanda. USawuli wasesithi kumpristi: Buyisela isandla sakho\x + Nani 27.21.\x*.
\v 20 USawuli labo bonke abantu ababelaye basebebizelwa ndawonye bafika empini, khangela-ke, inkemba yalowo lalowo yayimelene lomakhelwane wakhe\x + Hlu. 7.22. 2 Lan. 20.23.\x*, isiyaluyalu esikhulu kakhulu\x + Dute. 28.20.\x*.
\v 21 LamaHebheru ayelamaFilisti njengakuqala, enyukela lawo enkambeni inhlangothi zonke, ngitsho lawo aphenduka ukuthi abe loIsrayeli owayeloSawuli loJonathani\x + 13.7.\x*.
\v 22 Kwathi amadoda wonke akoIsrayeli ayecatshe\x + 13.6. 14.11.\x* entabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + Josh. 24.33.\x* esezwile ukuthi amaFilisti ayabaleka, ngitsho lawo awanamathela ewalandela empini.
\v 23 Ngokunjalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamsindisa uIsrayeli ngalolosuku\x + Eks. 14.30.\x*; lempi yedlulela eBeti-Aveni\x + 13.5. Josh. 7.2.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Amadoda akoIsrayeli asekhathala ngalolosuku\x + 13.6.\x*, ngoba uSawuli wafungisa abantu esithi: Kaqalekiswe umuntu odla ukudla kuze kube ntambama, ukuze ngiziphindiselele ezitheni zami. Ngakho kakho ebantwini owanambitha ukudla\x + Josh. 6.26.\x*.
\v 25 Bonke \add abe\add*lizwe basebefika ehlathini\x + Gen. 41.57. 1 Kho. 10.24. Dute. 9.28. Mat. 3.5.\x*; njalo kwakuloluju phezu kobuso bomhlabathi\x + Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\v 26 Lapho abantu bengena ehlathini, khangela, uluju lwathonta; kodwa kakho loyedwa owasa isandla sakhe emlonyeni wakhe, ngoba abantu besaba isifungo\x + Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\v 27 Kodwa uJonathani wayengezwanga lapho uyise efungisa abantu; ngakho welula isihloko somqwayi owawusesandleni sakhe, wasigxamuza ehlangeni lwenyosi, wasesisa isandla sakhe emlonyeni wakhe, lamehlo akhe aqaqabuka.
\v 28 Omunye wabantu wasephendula wathi: Uyihlo ubafungisile lokubafungisa abantu esithi: Uqalekisiwe umuntu odla ukudla lamuhla. Abantu basebephele amandla\x + Hlu. 18.14.\x*.
\v 29 UJonathani wasesithi: Ubaba ulihluphile ilizwe; ake libone ukuthi amehlo ami aseqaqabuke njani, ngoba nginambithe ingcosana yaloluluju.
\v 30 Kudlula kangakanani aluba abantu bebedlile lokudla lamuhla okwempango yezitha zabo abayitholayo? Ngoba khathesi ukubulala kakubanga kukhulu phakathi kwamaFilisti.
\v 31 Basebetshaya amaFilisti ngalolosuku kusukela eMikimashi\x + 13.2.\x* kuze kube seAjaloni\x + Josh. 10.12.\x*. Abantu basebephele amandla kakhulu.
\v 32 Abantu basebetheleka empangweni; bathatha izimvu, lezinkabi, lamathole enkomo, bakuhlabela emhlabathini\x + 15.19.\x*; abantu bakudla kanye legazi\x + Levi 3.17.\x*.
\v 33 Basebemtshela uSawuli besithi: Khangela, abantu bayona eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngokudla kanye legazi. Wasesithi: Lenze ngokungathembeki; giqelani kimi ilitshe elikhulu lamuhla.
\v 34 USawuli wasesithi: Zihlakazeni phakathi kwabantu lithi kibo: Sondezani kimi, ngulowo lalowo inkabi yakhe, langulowo lalowo imvu yakhe, lizihlabele lapha, lidle; njalo lingoni eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngokudla kanye legazi\x + Eks. 12.3.\x*. Ngakho bonke abantu basondeza, ngulowo lalowo inkabi yakhe ngesandla sakhe ngalobobusuku, bazihlaba khona.
\v 35 USawuli waseyakhela iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi; kwakulilathi lokuqala alakhela iN\nd kosi\x + 14.33. 7.17.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 36 USawuli wasesithi: Asehleni silandele amaFilisti ebusuku, siwaphange kuze kube yikukhanya kokusa, singatshiyi lamuntu kiwo. Basebesithi: Yenza konke okuhle emehlweni akho. Kodwa umpristi wathi: Asisondeleni lapha kuNkulunkulu\x + 14.3,18,19.\x*.
\v 37 USawuli wasebuza kuNkulunkulu \add wathi\add*: Ngehle ngilandele amaFilisti yini? Uzawanikela esandleni sikaIsrayeli yini? Kodwa kamphendulanga ngalolosuku\x + 28.6.\x*.
\v 38 USawuli wasesithi: Sondelani lapha lonke bakhokheli babantu, lazi libone ukuthi lesisono sikukuphi lamuhla\x + 10.19. Josh. 7.14.\x*.
\v 39 Ngoba kuphila kukaJehova owasindisa uIsrayeli\x + Ruthe 3.13.\x*, lanxa kungaba kuJonathani indodana yami, isibili uzakufa lokufa. Kodwa kakho loyedwa owamphendulayo ebantwini bonke.
\v 40 Wasesithi kuIsrayeli wonke: Banini nganxanye lina, mina-ke loJonathani indodana yami sizakuba nganxanye. Abantu basebesithi kuSawuli: Yenza okuhle emehlweni akho.
\v 41 Ngakho uSawuli wathi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Phana opheleleyo\x + Hlu. 20.9.\x*. UJonathani loSawuli basebebanjwa, kodwa abantu baphunyuka\x + 10.20,21. Josh. 7.16.\x*.
\v 42 USawuli wasesithi: Yenzani \add inkatho\add* yokuphosa phakathi kwami loJonathani indodana yami. UJonathani wasebanjwa.
\v 43 USawuli wasesithi kuJonathani: Ngitshela okwenzileyo\x + Josh. 7.19.\x*. UJonathani wasemtshela wathi: Oqotho nginambithe ngesihloko somqwayi obusesandleni sami imbijana yoluju; khangela ngi\add lapha\add*, sengizakufa\x + 14.27.\x*!
\v 44 USawuli wasesithi: UNkulunkulu kenze njalo langokunjalo engezelele\x + Ruthe 1.17.\x*; ngoba uzakufa lokufa, Jonathani\x + 14.39.\x*.
\v 45 Kodwa abantu bathi kuSawuli: Uzakufa yini uJonathani, owenze lolusindiso olukhulu koIsrayeli? Kakube khatshana! Kuphila kukaJehova\x + Ruthe 3.13.\x*, kakuyikuwela emhlabathini lolulodwa unwele lwekhanda lakhe, ngoba usebenze loNkulunkulu lamuhla. Ngakho abantu bamhlenga uJonathani ukuthi angafi\x + 2 Sam. 14.11. 1 Kho. 1.52. Mat. 10.30. Luka 12.7. 21.18. Seb. 27.34.\x*.
\v 46 USawuli wasesenyuka esuka ekulandeleni amaFilisti; amaFilisti asesiya endaweni yawo.
\p
\v 47 USawuli wasethatha ubukhosi phezu kukaIsrayeli, walwa emelene lezitha zakhe zonke inhlangothi zonke, emelene loMowabi, njalo emelene labantwana bakoAmoni\x + 11.11.\x*, njalo emelene loEdoma, njalo emelene lamakhosi eZoba\x + 2 Sam. 8.3.\x*, njalo emelene lamaFilisti; laloba ngaphi lapho aphendukela khona wayejezisa.
\v 48 Wenza ngobuqhawe wasetshaya amaAmaleki\x + 15.3-7.\x*, wakhulula uIsrayeli esandleni somphangi wakhe.
\p
\v 49 Lamadodana kaSawuli ayengoJonathani loIshivi, loMaliki-Shuwa\x + 31.2. 2 Sam. 2.8-10. 1 Lan. 8.33. 9.39.\x*; lamabizo amadodakazi akhe amabili \add yila\add*: Ibizo lezibulo lalinguMerabi\x + 18.17-19.\x*, lebizo lencinyane linguMikhali\x + 18.20,27. 19.12. 25.44. 2 Sam. 3.14. 6.20-23. 21.8.\x*.
\v 50 Lebizo lomkaSawuli lalinguAhinowama indodakazi kaAhimahazi; lebizo lenduna yebutho lakhe lalinguAbhineri indodana kaNeri\x + 2 Sam. 2.8.\x*, uyise omncinyane kaSawuli\x + 10.14.\x*.
\v 51 Njalo uKishi wayenguyise kaSawuli\x + 9.1.\x*, loNeri uyise kaAbhineri wayeyindodana kaAbiyeli\x + 9.1.\x*.
\v 52 Njalo kwakukhona impi enzima lamaFilisti zonke izinsuku zikaSawuli; lapho uSawuli ebona indoda elamandla loba iqhawe, wayezibuthela yona\x + 8.11.\x*.
